snippet.title: Metal Gear Solid 4 - Uncut 2005 Reveal Trailer in 1080P/60FPS
snippet.description: Here is the uncut 2005 reveal trailer for Metal Gear Solid 4, in glorious 60 FPS. While this is from a standard-def PlayStation Magazine DVD, It was upscaled to HD in a PS3.
